{"id":166,"parent_id":158,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":166,"title":"Deuteronomy 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Deut.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord tested the children of Israel in the wilderness for forty years—Eating manna taught them that man lives by the word of God—Their clothing did not wear out—The Lord chastened them—If they serve other gods, they will perish."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.1","order":"02.06.008.14958"},["b","1"],"All the commandments which I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"command"],"thee this day shall ye observe to do, that ye may live, and multiply, and go in and possess the land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"sware unto your fathers."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.2","order":"02.06.008.14959"},["b","2"],"And thou shalt remember all the way which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God led thee these forty years in the wilderness, to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"humble"],"thee,",["i","and"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"prove"],"thee, to know what",["i","was"],"in thine heart, whether thou wouldest keep his commandments, or no."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.3","order":"02.06.008.14960"},["b","3"],"And he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"humbled"],"thee, and suffered thee to hunger, and fed thee with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"manna"],", which thou knewest not, neither did thy fathers know; that he might make thee know that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"man"],"doth not live by",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"bread"],"only, but by every",["i",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_3e"},"word"]],"that proceedeth out of the mouth of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"doth man live."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.4","order":"02.06.008.14961"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Thy"],"raiment waxed not old upon thee, neither did thy foot swell, these forty years."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.5","order":"02.06.008.14962"},["b","5"],"Thou shalt also consider in thine heart, that, as a man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"chasteneth"],"his son,",["i","so"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God chasteneth thee."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.6","order":"02.06.008.14963"},["b","6"],"Therefore thou shalt keep the commandments of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"walk"],"in his ways, and to fear him."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.7","order":"02.06.008.14964"},["b","7"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God bringeth thee into a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"good"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"land"],", a land of brooks of water, of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"fountains"],"and depths that spring out of valleys and hills;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.8","order":"02.06.008.14965"},["b","8"],"A land of wheat, and barley, and vines, and fig trees, and pomegranates; a land of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"oil olive"],", and honey;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.9","order":"02.06.008.14966"},["b","9"],"A land wherein thou shalt eat bread without scarceness, thou shalt not lack any",["i","thing"],"in it; a land whose stones",["i","are"],"iron, and out of whose hills thou mayest dig",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"brass"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.10","order":"02.06.008.14967"},["b","10"],"When thou hast eaten and art full, then thou shalt bless the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God for the good land which he hath given thee."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.11","order":"02.06.008.14968"},["b","11"],"Beware that thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"forget"],"not the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, in not keeping his commandments, and his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"judgments"],", and his statutes, which I command thee this day:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.12","order":"02.06.008.14969"},["b","12"],"Lest",["i","when"],"thou hast eaten and art full, and hast built goodly houses, and dwelt",["i","therein;"]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.13","order":"02.06.008.14970"},["b","13"],"And",["i","when"],"thy herds and thy flocks multiply, and thy silver and thy gold is multiplied, and all that thou hast is multiplied;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.14","order":"02.06.008.14971"},["b","14"],"Then thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"heart"],"be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"lifted up"],", and thou",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"forget"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, which brought thee forth out of the land of Egypt, from the house of bondage;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.15","order":"02.06.008.14972"},["b","15"],"Who led thee through that great and terrible wilderness,",["i","wherein were"],"fiery",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"serpents"],", and scorpions, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"drought"],", where",["i","there was"],"no water; who brought thee forth",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"water"],"out of the rock of flint;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.16","order":"02.06.008.14973"},["b","16"],"Who fed thee in the wilderness with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"manna"],", which thy fathers knew not, that he might humble thee, and that he might",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"prove"],"thee, to do thee good at thy latter end;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.17","order":"02.06.008.14974"},["b","17"],"And thou say in thine heart, My power and the might of",["i","mine"],"hand hath gotten me this wealth."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.18","order":"02.06.008.14975"},["b","18"],"But thou shalt remember the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God: for",["i","it is"],"he that giveth thee power to get",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"wealth"],", that he may establish his covenant which he sware unto thy fathers, as",["i","it is"],"this day."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.19","order":"02.06.008.14976"},["b","19"],"And it shall be, if thou do at all forget the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"walk"],"after other",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"gods"],", and serve them, and worship them, I testify against you this day that ye shall surely",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"perish"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.20","order":"02.06.008.14977"},["b","20"],"As the nations which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"destroyeth before your face, so shall ye perish; because ye would not be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"obedient"],"unto the voice of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.1a","order":"02.06.008.14978"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.20"},"D&C 93:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.2a","order":"02.06.008.14980"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.2b","order":"02.06.008.14982"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/15.25.23-26"},"Ex. 15:25 (23–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/32.31.20,22,31"},"2 Chr. 32:31 (20, 22, 31)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.3a","order":"02.06.008.14984"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.3b","order":"02.06.008.14986"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/9.20"},"Neh. 9:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.28"},"1 Ne. 17:28"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.3c","order":"02.06.008.14988"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/4.4"},"Matt. 4:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/4.4"},"Luke 4:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.44.43-44"},"D&C 84:44 (43–44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.3d","order":"02.06.008.14990"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bread"},"TG Bread"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bread-of-life"},"Bread of Life"],"."],["div",{"id":"3e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.3e","order":"02.06.008.14992"},["b","3e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-study-of"},"Scriptures, Study of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.4a","order":"02.06.008.14994"},["b","4a"],["span.small","OR"],"Your clothing did not wear out."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.5a","order":"02.06.008.14996"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastening"},"TG Chastening"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.6a","order":"02.06.008.14998"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.7a","order":"02.06.008.15000"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.8"},"Ex. 3:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.7b","order":"02.06.008.15002"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-land-of"},"TG Israel, Land of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.7c","order":"02.06.008.15004"},["b","7c"],["span.small","OR"],"springs and water recesses.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/33.28"},"Deut. 33:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.8a","order":"02.06.008.15006"},["b","8a"],["span.small","IE"],"olive trees."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.9a","order":"02.06.008.15008"},["b","9a"],["span.small","HEB"],"bronze, copper, brass."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.11a","order":"02.06.008.15010"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2.1-6"},"Hel. 12:2 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.11b","order":"02.06.008.15012"},["b","11b"],["span.small","HEB"],"ordinances."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.14a","order":"02.06.008.15014"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pride"},"TG Pride"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.14b","order":"02.06.008.15016"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/14.10"},"2 Kgs. 14:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.14c","order":"02.06.008.15018"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ingratitude"},"TG Ingratitude"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.15a","order":"02.06.008.15020"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/21.6.4-9"},"Num. 21:6 (4–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.41"},"1 Ne. 17:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/9.33.31-33"},"Ether 9:33 (31–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.15b","order":"02.06.008.15022"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/drought"},"TG Drought"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.15c","order":"02.06.008.15024"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.29"},"1 Ne. 17:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.16a","order":"02.06.008.15026"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.6.5-8"},"Hosea 13:6 (5–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.16b","order":"02.06.008.15028"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.18a","order":"02.06.008.15030"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.19a","order":"02.06.008.15032"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.19b","order":"02.06.008.15034"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.19c","order":"02.06.008.15036"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.11.5-17"},"Ezek. 5:11 (5–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.20a","order":"02.06.008.15038"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."]]}
